title: N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 12 §§ 61-3.7 - Reporting and recordkeeping

N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 12 §§ 61-3.7 - Reporting and recordkeeping

State Regulations

The reporting requirements of section
61-1.7
of this Part shall apply
under this Subpart and shall include the name of the owner of the
crane. Notes
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 12
§§
61-3.7

State regulations are updated quarterly; we currently have two versions available. Below is a
comparison between our most recent version and the prior quarterly release. More comparison features will be added as we have more versions to compare. No prior version found.
